  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had-- we had long journey down-- down on the Nile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the boss-- well, there was organized-- organized tours, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was-- most of the time it was so-- and we visited the-- the Pyramids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There I found out what kind of naughty-- really naughty and-- [LAUGHS] --dirty girl-- she-- she climbed on the top of the Great Pyramid.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I did too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she beat me to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And specially coming down, it was worse coming down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because of the-- of the gravitation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You could feel it when you were up and when you were in the tower and just look out, it's a different thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when you are in an open, up there, on an 800-feet-tall pyramid, on the top of it, and that was about that to that, square, on the top.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from that-- the drape, they pulled-- pulled on the marble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used it to build mosque with and so on, and in Cairo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you could-- you could climb it, because it was like-- like this, like steps, you see?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- she climbed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] On the next tape, I will ask you more questions about this period in Cairo.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
